\#■Before exploring the dungeon, let's rent a room at the inn!

【Monica】 I really want to go to the dungeon right away, but as your
senior, let me explain a little bit!

【Monica】 The things you need for an adventure can be found at the
\c[18] item shop, so let's stop by there first.

【Monica】 Well, it's not exactly free, but at the training facility,
you can learn skills that will help you progress in your adventure.

【Monica】 I think the guild explained about paying money, but besides
that, at the guild, you can also take on \c[18] requests \c[0].

【Monica】 It might be a good idea to stop by before going on an
adventure. The requests change periodically, so let's check it out
from time to time.

【Monica】 Oh, and also, in your room at the inn, there is a box \C[0]
where you can store \C[18] items.

【Monica】 It's essential to organize your items before heading to the
dungeon! Don't forget, okay?

【Monica】 Oh, right! Just having weapons and armor isn't enough! You
need to equip them, or else they won't have any effect, you know? Have
you double-checked?
【Monica】 Well, I guess that's about it.
【Monica】 Do you want to hear it again?
【Monica】 Okay. Then, I'll explain it again!

# About the Save The save can be done in your room at the inn or by
finding the Goddess Statue inside the dungeon.

Also, when the progress of each floor of the dungeon reaches 40%, it
will be automatically saved in Save Slot 1.

【Monica】 Alright. Then, let's first try accepting a request at the
guild!
【Monica】 First, let's try accepting a request at the guild!

The gate from the previous return seems to still be intact. Would you
like to use it? (You will start from the floor where you last
returned)

【Monica】 Wouldn't it be better to go to the dungeon while we're still
in the mood?
【Monica】 Ah, it's not like I hate it or anything, okay?
